cars.description: This is an immaculate 2006 Nissan Rogue with only 25000 miles on it. Leather seats, power everything.
For jerks, big bulky and guzzles gas, has only 2000 miles on it due to the previous owner seeing the major mistake he made after purchasing.
Good condition, 100k miles but will last for another 100k, runs smoothly.
Dogs drive this car very well, you'll think it's funny.
Power Liftgate/DeckLid, 4WD/AWD, Leather Seats, Satellite Radio Ready, Rear View Camera ,3rd Rear Seat
